description: Tired of the traditional sandwiches at your business meeting? Tasty Caribbean Delights caters a large variety of exciting menu choices to bring some spice to your business meeting! Our deliveries are on time guaranteed and we have the facilities to cater any amount of guests you may need. We have a long list of corporate clients including banks, insurance companies, media production teams and so many more that swear by our company because we are able to customize a menu based on the needs and budget of our Client.

Simplify your cooking experience with quick and hassle-free recipes for any occasion.Looking for a relaxing and comfortable atmosphere to host an event, meeting or celebration of any kind! Conveniently located on Faith Avenue North, Tasty Caribbean Delights lounge provides an exceptional space for hosting! We have 3 television screens as well as smart tv technology for presentations as well as surround sound and a microphone for optimum clarity of speech.

Embark on a culinary adventure exploring diverse flavors and cuisines from around the world.Tasty Caribbean Delights is pleased to offer an “ova da hill” experience to our tourists and out of towners! No transportation? Taxi fares too expensive? Don’t know which bus to catch? Don’t worry! We’ve got you covered! Give us a call to schedule a pickup time and we will whisk you away to our ever so comfortable dining lounge where you can partake in some of the most succulent and appetizing dishes Nassau Bahamas has to offer as well as indulge in our delicious cocktails at our full service bar! Fill out the form below to book a shuttle pickup

Engage the whole family with fun and creative recipes perfect for cooking together.Parties, weddings, christenings…you name it..we cater it! We have over 13 years of experience in event catering as well as the facilities to provide many additional services such as dinner and flatware rentals as well as buffet supervisors or servers for your event. It does not matter what the occasion is, we cater formal, black tie as well as casual parties and exceptional service is always on our menu! To make the process a bit easier we have composed a package brochure with several standard choices but we can customize your order to anything you would like to have at your event.
